{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "camrie-cloudmr-brain-2026",
		"name": "CAMRIE – CloudMR Brain",
		"description": "End-to-end flow for scheduling a CAMRIE MRI simulation via the CloudMR Brain API.\n\n## Flow\n1. **Login** → get `id_token`\n2. **Upload files** (rho, t1, t2, sequence) via multipart upload\n3. **Queue Job** → submit the simulation task\n4. **Poll Pipeline** → check status until completed/failed\n\n## Variables\nSet `email`, `password`, and optionally `api_base` in the collection variables before running.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
